{"id": 2650, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得日常对话中，我们应该避免哪些习惯性“暴力沟通”？", "description": "暴力沟通，即，一言不合就 judge 人，分分钟上纲上线。（题图来自 iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 4206, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201811281023427xXUF9q0Ms1uApiN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-03T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 313600, "content": "指出对方毛病时以“你怎么总是”开头", "image": null, "praise_count": 708, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 314368, "content": "请大家一起解决问题，而不是解决提出问题的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424449}, {"id": 315648, "content": "缺乏尊重\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527772}, {"id": 314625, "content": "什么都不懂，还乱开腔……虽然是老公开玩笑说的，但是真的很伤自尊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523070}, {"id": 314370, "content": "你给我……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522149}, {"id": 315650, "content": "对人不对事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525718}, {"id": 314371, "content": "说什么，问什么都被回一句“不然呢”，“你以为呢”", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522151}, {"id": 317699, "content": "那又怎么样？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536533}, {"id": 314884, "content": "你这智商..", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403926}, {"id": 314373, "content": "哪有那么多为什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334007}, {"id": 314374, "content": "我错了 对不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334007}, {"id": 314375, "content": "“怎么可能…？”\n“你咋知道的…？”\n“谁说的…？”\n“你怎么会知道的…？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1518395}, {"id": 314376, "content": "道德绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461866}, {"id": 314377, "content": "回答问题的第一句：“对啊”（上扬调）", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296626}, {"id": 314378, "content": "行行行，就这样吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303197}, {"id": 314634, "content": "喔唷，开不起玩笑哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43811}, {"id": 314635, "content": "无奈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523081}, {"id": 314380, "content": "打断别人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641724}, {"id": 314381, "content": "我不管你……开头", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499732}, {"id": 314382, "content": "心平气和，夜郎自大可不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427152}, {"id": 314383, "content": "我怎么知道你噢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522180}, {"id": 319503, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543993}, {"id": 314384, "content": "冷暴力", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516606}, {"id": 314385, "content": "无论你说啥 他总是说\"不，我觉得....\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516527}, {"id": 314386, "content": "“也不是吧……”神烦，为了反驳而反驳，又不能让人信服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302582}, {"id": 314898, "content": "是真的捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509566}, {"id": 314387, "content": "认为问题永远出在对方身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507908}, {"id": 315667, "content": "没事就“.....”，点你**", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 314388, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519342}, {"id": 314389, "content": "“你能不能别.......”你能不能别闹了，你能不能别说话，你能不能憋吵了，你能不能别说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522195}, {"id": 315414, "content": "百度很方便非要一遍一遍的问", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448244}, {"id": 314392, "content": "对于和你交谈时走神又不回应的人，停止交谈，并离开，不要生气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486704}, {"id": 314396, "content": "“你懂我在说什么吧？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468010}, {"id": 314399, "content": "你说话就不能有点逻辑吗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197096}, {"id": 315424, "content": "-你先听我说一句。\n-我知道你要说什么！你听我说。\n(内心OS:你知道就有鬼了…)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344221}, {"id": 314403, "content": "能自己解决的事情绝不求人 \n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 314659, "content": "不听解释，固执己见，强加自己的意识给他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1521421}, {"id": 314915, "content": "那你让他去做吧，我不管", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524167}, {"id": 314404, "content": "语言绑架", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522213}, {"id": 314917, "content": "都是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473906}, {"id": 314918, "content": "自带贬低对方人格的表达方式（很熟的朋友开玩笑除外）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 314407, "content": "那我怎么样？\n……", "image": "img/option/option/201812031753304tYsDf9l1hkbCOaJ", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522224}, {"id": 314408, "content": "生气就说“NMSL”", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490853}, {"id": 314920, "content": "强迫对方接受自己的观点，一言不合就动怒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 314409, "content": "不回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498037}, {"id": 323374, "content": "不管别人说什么，总是开头就说“不是，这件事是这样的”我特么观点跟你一样啊，你不是个蛋，到底有没有认真听我说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561470}, {"id": 314672, "content": "不是，我开玩笑的。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479721}, {"id": 314674, "content": "你喜欢的…我可欣赏不来 太高雅 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523227}, {"id": 314676, "content": "就应该咋咋咋地 你这样不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523227}, {"id": 314424, "content": "我不是说过？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198490}]}